# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(2^N)$$ 

- Space complexity: $$O(2^N)$$

# Approach-2 Memoization (Gets Submitted!)

As Usual, In Memoization we try to reduce number of recursive calls by storing them.
Here only two values are changing at each state, so we define a `hashMap` to store the previous computations to use them whenever we encounter the previous state.
This helps us to reduce the number of calls and Reduce the Time Complexity from $$O(2^N)$$ to $$O(N^2)$$

