# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
use hashmaps to store the indices of stones. and accordingly decide the jump.Just remember the jump should be forward.

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
O(N^2).

- Space complexity:
<!-- Add your space complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
